==毒性==
[[File:Raphides_from_variegated_ivy.jpg|thumb]]
绿萝的毒性来自于其汁液中的{{le|针晶体|Raphide}}，这也是许多[[天南星科|天南星科]]植物的特征。这些不易溶解于水的[[草酸钙|草酸钙]]针晶体会对进食者的口腔、食道等软组织细胞带来物理性损伤，因此人或动物误食绿萝的枝叶，可以引起口腔刺痛、呕吐、吞咽困难等等。皮肤接触其汁液也会产生刺痛感等反应。<ref name="aspca_site">{{cite web|url=http://www.aspca.org/pet-care/poison-control/plants/devils_ivy.html |title=Devils Ivy |accessdate=2009-03-11 |work=ASPCA.org }}</ref><ref>[http://informahealthcare.com/doi/abs/10.1081/CLT-44721 Outbreak of Food-borne Illness Associated with Plant Material Containing Raphides]. Informa Healthcare.</ref><ref>ASPCA (2009). Taro. ASPCA official website: Animal Poison Control Center. Retrieved on 2009-12-07 from: http://www.aspca.org/pet-care/poison-control/plants/taro-1.html</ref><ref>Wrongdiagnosis.com (2009). Plant poisoning – Calcium oxalate crystals. Wrongdiagnosis.com retrieved on 2009-12-07 from: http://www.wrongdiagnosis.com/p/plant_poisoning_calcium_oxalate_crystals/intro.htm</ref>

==入侵物种==
[[File:Epipremnum_aureum_in_Udawattakele.jpg|thumb]]{{le|乌达瓦塔凯勒保护区|Udawatta Kele Sanctuary}}内，绿萝占据了大片树林。]]
绿萝作为观赏植物被人类带到世界各地，而在一些非原生地的[[热带雨林|热带雨林]]中，因缺乏环境和其他物种的压制，绿萝得以大量繁殖，成为[[入侵物种|入侵物种]]。例如在[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]的雨林中，绿萝过度生长，进而干扰到当地生态平衡<ref name="article">{{cite web |url=http://thakshana.nsf.ac.lk/pdf/JNSF26-34/JNSF29_1&2/JNSF29_1&2_35.pdf |title='W. De Costa, H. Hitanayake and I. Dharmawardena, "A Physiological Investigation into the Invasive Behaviour of Some Plant Species in a Mid-Country Forest Reserve in Sri Lanka" |accessdate=2009-03-11 |work=JNSFSL, 2001, 29 (1 & 2):35–50 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722145720/http://thakshana.nsf.ac.lk/pdf/JNSF26-34/JNSF29_1%262/JNSF29_1%262_35.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-22 }}</ref>。[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]于1999年将绿萝列入“入侵物种”名录<ref>USDA Natural Resources Conservation Service). [http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=EPPI Plants Profile]</ref>。

